{{zh-forms|[[荳懆･ｿ]]|[[譚ｱ]][[隘ｿ]]}}
==Mandarin==
===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|[ tﾊ看桐･ﾋ･ﾉ品ﾋ･ﾋ･ ]}} ''east and west''
*{{IPA|[ tﾊ看桐･ﾋ･ﾉ品 ]}} ''thing''

====Etymology====
Literally, the two [[morpheme]]s that compose this word mean ''east'' and ''west''

===Noun===
{{cmn-noun|t|pin=dﾅ肱gxﾄｫ|pint=dong1xi1|tra=譚ｱ隘ｿ|sim=荳懆･ｿ|rs=譛ｨ04}}
# [[east]] and [[west]], from east to west

{{cmn-noun|t|pin=dﾅ肱gxi|pint=dong1xi|tra=譚ｱ隘ｿ|sim=荳懆･ｿ|rs=譛ｨ04}}
 
# [[something]]; [[thing]]

===Usage notes===
*'''譚ｱ隘ｿ''' means thing in a physical sense, whereas [[莠区ュ]] means thing in an abstract sense.

===See also===
*(''Min Nan'') [[迚ｩ莉ｶ]] ([[miﾌ紘-kiﾄ≫∩|mi{{unicode|ﾌ閤}h-kiﾄ≫∩]]) ''something; thing''

