==Min Nan==
===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|[ taﾅ桐ｧﾋｧsaiﾋ･ﾋ･ ]}}

===Noun===
{{nan-noun|t|poj=tang-sai|pojt=tang1sai1|tra=譚ｱ隘ｿ|sim=荳懆･ｿ|rs=譛ｨ04}}
# [[east]] and [[west]], from east to west

===Usage notes===
*Unlike Mandarin, '''譚ｱ隘ｿ''' does not mean ''something'' or ''thing'' in Min Nan.  Use [[迚ｩ莉ｶ]] ([[miﾌ紘-kiﾄ≫∩|mi{{unicode|ﾌ閤}h-kiﾄ≫∩]]) instead.  For ''thing'' in the abstract sense, use [[莉｣隱珪] ([[tﾄ（-chﾃｬ]]).